text: Saint-Grégoire may refer to the following communes in France: *Saint-Grégoire, Ille-et-Vilaine, in the Ille-et-Vilaine department *Saint-Grégoire, Tarn, in the Tarn department *Saint-Grégoire-d'Ardennes, in the Charente-Maritime department *Saint-Grégoire-du-Vièvre, in the Eure department
title: Saint-Grégoire
